Pricilla Nanyang (Priscila Nyanyang ma ọ bụ Priscilla Nyayang Joseph Kuch) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Sudan. Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka osote minista maka okike, ụmụaka na ọdịmma ọha na eze yana minista na-enweghị ọfịs.
Nanyang nwetara nzere bachelọ nke ọgwụ na ịwa ahụ na 1978 na Mahadum nke Khartoum
Ọ natara Masters of Community Medicine site na 1987 kwa site na Mahadum nke Khartoum.

N'agbata afọ 2005 na afọ 2010 ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye otu Sudan People's Liberation Movement (SPLM) nke National Assembly na onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Na-ahụ Maka Ihe Ndị Ruuru Mmadụ na National Parliament. N'afọ 2007, Nanyang sonyere n'òtù SPLM iji gbalịa ma mee ka mkparịta ụka udo dị na Darfur dị mfe. Nanyang bụ otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị asaa a họpụtara na kansụl South Sudan na June 2010. A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ Minista na-enweghị ọfịs na Cabinet nke South Sudan na 10 Julaị 2011

Dị ka Minista na-enweghị ọfịs, Nanyang duziri ọrụ nyocha izu asatọ, nke a na-akpọ "Nnyocha zuru oke nke Gọọmentị South Sudan", iji mụọ otú Gọọmentụ South Sudan si arụ ọrụ kemgbe e guzobere ya na 2005.
Ọ bụkwa onye bụbu osote minista maka okike, ụmụaka na ọdịmma ọha na eze

N'afọ 2014, ọ haziri nzukọ nke ụmụ nwanyị na-ahụ maka udo na Juba "iji kwalite ebumnuche nke udo, ọgwụgwọ na ime udo". Dị ka osote minista, ọ gara New York City na 2013 maka Nzukọ nke 57 nke Commission on the Status of Women na mgbe ọ nọ na New York zutere mmemme na-ewu udo na ikike na Mahadum Columbia Institute for the Study of Human Rights. Ka ọ na-erule n'afọ 2015, Nanyang nwekwara ọkwa onye isi oche nke South Sudan Women Peace Network.
